<div id="review_3982365672" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3982365672" />
    <a title="Anubha (BooksFullOfLife, LifeFullOfBooks)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/24746974-anubha-booksfulloflife-lifefullofbooks"><img alt="Anubha (BooksFullOfLife, LifeFullOfBooks)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1588871963p2/24746974.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3982365672?book_show_action=true">May 18, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Anubha (BooksFullOfLife, LifeFullOfBooks)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Anubha (BooksFullOfLife, LifeFullOfBooks)" href="/user/show/24746974-anubha-booksfulloflife-lifefullofbooks">Anubha (BooksFullOfLife, LifeFullOfBooks)</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781534441934" href="/book/show/54238295-a-pho-love-story">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24746974-anubha-booksfulloflife-lifefullofbooks?shelf=family">family</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24746974-anubha-booksfulloflife-lifefullofbooks?shelf=romance">romance</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3982365672" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12748048932052655833">A book about rivaling restaurants, vietnamese phrases, cuisines, bitter past, forbidden love.<br/><br/>This book was fun to follow, glimpses of Vietnamese culture did slow down my reading. I didn&apos;t catch the phrases, I wish the english meaning were written in brackets. It was kinda annoying to not know what they meant or to google every few sentences later. <br/><br/>But I do understand Asian rivalry between two families. The fathers were mostly chill or showed their anger in a mellow manner while the mothers are a</span>
  <span id="freeText12748048932052655833" style="display:none">A book about rivaling restaurants, vietnamese phrases, cuisines, bitter past, forbidden love.<br /><br />This book was fun to follow, glimpses of Vietnamese culture did slow down my reading. I didn't catch the phrases, I wish the english meaning were written in brackets. It was kinda annoying to not know what they meant or to google every few sentences later. <br /><br />But I do understand Asian rivalry between two families. The fathers were mostly chill or showed their anger in a mellow manner while the mothers are all scream session ready, telling their children not to play together, very relatable. <br /><br />The restaurant rivalry wasnt overpowering, it was mostly the family rivalry which stood out. The two main characters Bao and Linh were written very realistically as well. <br /><br />The Asian preference of forcing their kid to be a engineer/doctor is v realistic too, not only restricted to Vietnam but most of the Asian countries. Opting for arts is mostly like committing a crime. There are exceptions ofc. <br /><br />I loved how the book makes me realize the sacrifices our parents make to give the comfort they never had. How hard they work to provide us with everything we need. Sometimes we forget all that our parents have done and continue to do for us &lt;3 &lt;3<br /><br />Overall, I enjoyed reading it.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12748048932052655833" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


